CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 2, 1961, pg. 20, reads: "Glamour Too! - Carol Thompson, local singer, surrounded by 'Newsies' in Sully Pool."
TitMainTitle: Singer Carol Thompson posing with boys, including Sherman Parker on left, Harold Wilkes on right, Louis Murrell Jr. on right in pool, and Donald "Muscles" Wilkes squatting on right, at Sully's Pool in South Park during Pittsburgh Courier newsboys picnic
